Dessins des écoles du Nord: dans les collections privées françaises, May-June 1974. Important exhibition. (No owners given of any of the drawings), 14. H. Bol, Paysage, pl. 15. Coll. part...figures perhaps by other hand; 21.J. Brueghel I (pl. 22) Bateaux et pêcheurs sur une rivière. Coll .part. cf Basrode (but different perspective; 22 J. Brueghel I (pl. 23) Village. Street with several figures, pigs a chickens signed and dated: Brueghel fecit 1616; 24 (pl. 25) Matthijs Cock: ??? draught of fishes (called 'Prédication de St. Pierre) with St. Peter in water, and Christ on the shore. Attrib. acceptable; R. Savery.
